    "image_with_text_FAfVaW": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_tfc8jA": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Q: </strong>How has motherhood influenced your personal style?</p><p><strong>A:</strong> I think just making sure I can move in everything comfortably but still feel like myself and feel put together. It’s a little bit like having a uniform.<br/></p><p><strong>Q: </strong>Do you have go-to outfits that make you feel confident on busy days?</p><p><strong>A: </strong>The things that I feel good in no matter what I am doing. Usually it’s a wide legged pant paired with a blouse or striped shirt of some kind along with a good coat. I believe that a good coat can fix any outfit.<br/></p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "text_tfc8jA"
      ],
